# Page Template: Dashboard

> Reference template for building dashboard/overview pages in {{ display_name }}.

## Purpose

The dashboard is the primary landing page after login. It provides an at-a-glance overview of key metrics, recent activity, and quick actions.

## Layout Structure

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Header / Navigation Bar                          │
├──────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┤
│          │  Page Title + Actions                  │
│          ├───────────┬───────────┬───────────────┤
│  Sidebar │  KPI Card │  KPI Card │  KPI Card     │
│          ├───────────┴───────────┴───────────────┤
│  (nav)   │  Main Chart / Visualization            │
│          ├───────────────────┬───────────────────┤
│          │  Recent Activity  │  Quick Actions     │
│          │  (table/list)     │  (shortcuts)       │
└──────────┴───────────────────┴───────────────────┘
```

## Components

### KPI Cards (Top Row)

- 3-4 key performance indicators
- Each card: metric label, current value, trend indicator (up/down/neutral)
- Click navigates to detail view

### Main Visualization

- Primary chart showing the most important trend
- Time range selector (7d / 30d / 90d)
- Responsive sizing

### Recent Activity

- Table or list of recent events/actions
- Columns: timestamp, type, summary, actor
- Paginated or virtualized for performance
- Row click navigates to detail page

### Quick Actions

- 3-5 most common actions as buttons/cards
- Examples: "Create New...", "View Reports", "Invite Team Member"

## States

| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Loading | Skeleton placeholders for each section |
| Empty | Welcome message with setup steps |
| Error | Error banner with retry action |
| Loaded | Full dashboard with data |

## Design Notes ({{ design_style }})

{% if design_style == "minimal-clean" %}
- White background, subtle gray borders between sections
- Single accent color for interactive elements
- Generous padding between cards
{% elif design_style == "corporate-professional" %}
- Light gray background, white content cards with shadow
- Blue accent for primary actions
- Dense but organized information layout
{% elif design_style == "playful-modern" %}
- Colorful gradient header area
- Rounded cards with colorful icons
- Animated number counters for KPIs
{% endif %}

## Data Requirements

- Endpoint: `GET /api/dashboard/summary`
- Response includes: KPIs, chart data, recent activity
- Cache: 60 seconds (dashboard is eventually consistent)

## Accessibility

- KPI cards are keyboard-navigable
- Chart has text alternative / data table fallback
- Color is not the only indicator for trends (use icons)
- Screen reader announces dynamic updates
